              "displayName": "Kam Kasravi",
              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
            },
            "body": "Thanks Steve, you beat me on extrapolating :) See my later comment. Yes I guess I'm suggesting a HDFS equivalent to ~/.m2 or ~/.ivy2.\n\n\n",
